docs {
  ## Get Department
  ดึงข้อมูลแผนกรายการเดียวตาม ID

  Retrieves a single department record by its unique identifier.


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "name": "Item Name"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

